column5: The boys are back on the Ice this morning
How thick is the ice? How hard is the wind blowing? What is the preferred bait? How FOW should somebody be fishing in?
Ice is 5" Not much wind SW 10k Buckshots , Rapala Jigs ,Jig a Wopper's , Swidish Pimples tipped with minnows 10 to 13 fow has been good ..  2 minute walk to the fish ...
Why should you care by the time you get here the bite will be off and the ice will have melted
Shouldn't you be tuning up your snowblower Mike?
